title: The Definitive Art Bell Collection (1993-2003)
description:
Here is a compilation of a lot of the stuff floating around on the internet. I have merged and renamed every show to the yyyy-mm-dd structure. I will be doing updates in the future and posting them in the description.

If you have any questions please contact me at http://willstare.com/art-bell-repository/

It is about 20gb, so please keep that in mind when you download. I will be seeding this torrent with a server, but I wouldn't mind a few seeds if ya'll are feeling generous. 

I am thinking about eventually releasing a 2004-2010 torrent of every show Art hosted.
